      <ul>
        <li>Layers: <b>cuticle</b> (outer), <b>cortex</b> (strength/pigment), <b>medulla</b> (may be absent).</li>
        <li>Phases: <b>Anagen</b> (growth), <b>Catagen</b> (transition), <b>Telogen</b> (rest/shedding).</li>
        <li><b>Porosity</b> = absorb moisture; <b>Elasticity</b> = stretch & return; <b>Texture</b> = strand diameter.</li>
        <li>Bonds: <b>Hydrogen</b> (water/heat), <b>Salt</b> (pH), <b>Disulfide</b> (chemical).</li>
        <li>Melanin: <b>Eumelanin</b> (brown/black), <b>Pheomelanin</b> (red/blonde).</li>
      </ul>
    </details>
